{"books":[{"id":"whb","name":"文汇报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"国庆感怀","authors":["郭非"],"dates":[{"year":1981,"month":10,"day":1}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"郭非"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卅二年前战浦东，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五星红旗血染红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出师抗美风华茂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弹雨枪林雪满弓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"归国凯旋甲未解，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"峥嵘岁月正英雄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人欢马叫奔腾急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处神州颂东风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁知极左思潮起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缁衣铁锁雾重重。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紫金山上花落泪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淮北平原泣晚虹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身经浩劫心更苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河山满眼尽朦胧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平地一声惊雷响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钓鱼台前惩四凶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年苦难随云散，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三载图强唱大同。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燕语莺歌花似锦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尧天舜日又重逢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑看绿杨拂绿水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰收五谷喜工农。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全球反霸风云涌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挺立葱葱雪后松。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四化宏图实现日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国庆勿忘祭毛公。"}],"comments":[],"origin":"","comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}